<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_517" id="258r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_517_r1l18">Graf Johanſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r1l19">von wertheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_517_r1l20"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vns ewr edell
                            <expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat von Dyetrich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r1l21">wẏſentawers vnd des tags wegen als ewr gnade mit Jm
                        leiſten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r1l22">wölle etc <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd laſſen
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r1l23">vviſſen / daʒ cʒu der cʒeit vil
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Rats auſʒen <del rend="strikethrough">
                            vnd niht anheim </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r1l25">ſein / Alſo / daʒ vvir <add><ab facs="#facs_517_r1l24"><expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab></add>
<expan>nyemand<ex>en</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>gehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mügen / der darcʒu
                            darcʒu </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r1l26"><expan>gehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mügen / den vvir
                        darcʒu ſchicken / So dunkt vns auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r1l27">daʒ des kein not ſeẏ / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vvir </del>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden <del rend="strikethrough"> wol </del>
