                        baſʒ <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r1l29">vnd bıten <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell / daʒ Jr
                        vns des niht für v̈bell habt / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r1l30">wo vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden lieb vnd
                        dinſt <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möhte<ex>n</ex></expan> / das </ab>
